articles.title: US loses to Sweden on penalty kicks in its earliest Women's World Cup exit ever - The Associated Press
articles.description: The United States played its best game of this Women’s World Cup and it wasn’t good enough to stop the two-time reigning champions from being eliminated in the round of 16. The Americans’ bid to win an unprecedented third consecutive title ended Sunday on pen…
